cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a GAN-based model for image quality assessment, which involves image restoration and feature extraction. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the model involves adversarial training and optimization, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
